you say:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
Xaanru's post suggesting that if someone wasn't on the list, swooped in at the last minute, and aggro'ed the spawn first, then it's just fine as long as they didn't break any Verant rules really bugs me. That makes as much sense as saying that in RL all behavior is perfectly acceptable and it's fine to treat people however you want as long as you don't break the law. Sad. Screw the verant rules. It's about having respect for the effort of other players, not about whether or not some stupid verant rule was broken. <br>
